problem_info.title: 3427. Sum of Variable Length Subarrays
test_examples:
Example 1:  Input: nums = [2,3,1]  Output: 11  Explanation:  i	Subarray	Sum
0	nums[0] = [2]	2
1	nums[0 ... 1] = [2, 3]	5
2	nums[1 ... 2] = [3, 1]	4
Total Sum		11
The total sum is 11. Hence, 11 is the output.

Example 2:  Input: nums = [3,1,1,2]  Output: 13  Explanation:  i	Subarray	Sum
0	nums[0] = [3]	3
1	nums[0 ... 1] = [3, 1]	4
2	nums[1 ... 2] = [1, 1]	2
3	nums[1 ... 3] = [1, 1, 2]	4
Total Sum		13
The total sum is 13. Hence, 13 is the output.
